   717|/**
   718| * Import-smoke validation: transpiles and imports a changed backend module in the
   719| * REAL production runtime to prove the patch compiles and its import graph
   720| * resolves — a genuine, passing validation in a node-only container where the
   721| * bun test runner does not exist.
   722| *
   723| * Strategy 1 (primary): IN-PROCESS dynamic import. The backend already runs under
   724| * tsx (`node node_modules/tsx/dist/cli.mjs server.ts`), so the active loader
   725| * transpiles dynamically-imported `.ts` files with no child-process/PATH/specifier
