     1|/**
     2| * IVX Production Guard — self-healing rollback trigger.
     3| *
     4| * Observes the rolling failure rate from the incident store. If it crosses
     5| * the configured threshold over the configured window, triggers a Render
     6| * rollback to the previous deploy via the Render API, then records a
     7| * critical incident describing exactly what happened.
     8| *
     9| * Behavior is idempotent: a rollback in flight will not be retriggered until
    10| * the cooldown elapses.
    11| */
    12|
